ersonic"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 supersonic wave超声波"},{"type":"text","text":"ultrasonic frequency超声波频率"},{"type":"entry","text":"ultrasound /ˈʌltrəsaʊnd/ n. 超声（波）","headword":"ultrasound"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 ultrasound wave超声波"},{"type":"entry","text":"vocalization /ˌvoʊkələˈzeɪʃn/ n. 发声，发音","headword":"vocalization"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 vocal（声音的）+ization（行为的过程或结果）→发声"},{"type":"text","text":"wave motion波动"}]}]}